Some of my favourite bits were the competitions they ran. Every Drop In The Ocean, the &quot;win your own Spitting Image Puppet&quot; one  and the one where they gave away a shed were just some that pop to mind. I never won anything, mind.  <br /><br />Other than that, I loved the letters from foreign readers (Guilty laughs abound), Kindly Leave The Stage, Ernie The Psychotic Madman, the YS themed shoot-em-up that was given away, the brilliant reviews, and and and..... Hell, I just loved YS.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.ysrnry.co.uk/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=81">sweevo</a> — Fri Jul 01, 2011 12:33 am</p><hr />
